    <h1>Query Deserves Freshness (QDF): How Google's Freshness Signal Affects Your Rankings</h1>
    <p class="description">Query Deserves Freshness (QDF) is a Google algorithm that temporarily boosts fresh content for time-sensitive queries. Learn what triggers it and how to win those rankings.</p>
